profile:
Guliker Design Group Inc. is an Architectural, Dream Home, design & drafting company serving British Columbia since 2007. We use our extensive hands-on building expertise, cutting-edge visualization tools, and singular communication skills to help you translate your vision into breathtaking reality.

With over 15 year of hands-on building experience, you can be sure we know how an entire house is constructed. What we design, we are able to build. Understanding the ins and outs, of many types of buildings we are able to determine where costs can be reduced by providing another framing alternative, and provide the correct amount of details for the contractor to be able to construct the home without any delays.

For New Dream Homes we provide realistic renderings and a video walk-around so you can see every angle of your Dream Home before breaking ground.
